	<h1 class="title">一个游戏，就可以让各种人都来规划 Ta 的城市吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">宁卉</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-14 17:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22180/medium/22180.jpg?1455431086" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


